gisp test vectors
=================

Copyright (C) 2026 Uladzislau Bolbas <cmrtumilovic@gmail.com>

This directory holds known-answer test data for gisp: the binary container
files (v1_fixed.gisp, v1_streamed.gisp, v1_truncated.gisp) together with the
inputs used to produce them (plaintext, passphrase).  Because these are
binary or trivial data files that cannot carry their own copyright and
license notices, this README records them here, as recommended by the
GNU/Savannah documentation on copyright notices
(http://www.gnu.org/prep/maintain/html_node/Copyright-Notices.html).

